<plot>Obtuse Todd is a bizarre, off-putting comedy filled with twists and turns. Farley directs the film and also stars as the part-time musician, Todd Harding, who finds his life spiraling out of control when he starts receiving strange phone calls from a precocious young girl. Before long, he's juggling his time between the girl's overprotective father, a lovely co-worker and mysterious visitors looking for "stops."</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?406686</url></doc>
